Description: Low-level, data-driven core of boto3 (Avalan PPA transitive)
 botocore is the low-level interface to AWS services that the
 higher-level boto3 SDK builds on. This package is built for the
 Avalan PPA because aiobotocore (Avalan's `vendors` extra, reached
 via aioboto3) pins botocore to a tight `>= 1.40.46, < 1.40.62`
 window that neither Noble (1.34.46) nor the Debian snapshot pool
 (whose nearest higher version is 1.40.68, above the ceiling)
 satisfies. Pinned at 1.40.61, the top of the aiobotocore window.
